        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; line-height: 1.7;">Flexible engagement models designed for ambitious brands.</p>
        <div style="width: 40px; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent); margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(212,175,55,0.5);"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Featured DOMINATE Card -->
