      <div class="pricing-badge">Most Popular</div>
      <h3>DOMINATE™</h3>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 600px;">Our flagship brand-building system. Best for startups, SMBs and businesses looking to build, launch and scale with one dedicated growth partner.</p>
      
      <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 250px;">
          <p style="text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Setup Fee</p>
          <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0;">Starting from</p>
          <div class="pricing-price">₹125,000</div>
          <div class="pricing-usdt">or 1,389 USDT</div>
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 250px;">
          <p style="text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Monthly Growth Retainer</p>
          <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0;">Starting from</p>
          <div class="pricing-price" style="color: var(--blue-bright);">₹35,000<span style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);">/mo</span></div>
          <div class="pricing-usdt">or 389 USDT/mo</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">* Advertising budget is billed separately.</p>

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem;">
        <ul class="pricing-list" style="margin:0;">
