      <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 2.2rem;">Enterprise Solutions</h2>
      <h3 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Need something custom?</h3>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">We build tailored growth systems for funded startups, enterprise brands and rapidly scaling businesses.</p>
      
      <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
